 style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Mezkûr yazı ayrıca ekte sunulmaktadır.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Bilgilerini ve gereğini arz/rica ederim.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255); text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">OKAN ÖZTÜRK<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255); text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Genel Müdür a.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255); text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Genel Müdür Yardımcısı<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255);\"><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ek:</span></b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\